# Uptime


## Properties

Name | Type | Description | Notes
------------ | ------------- | ------------- | -------------
**billed** | **bool** | A Boolean value that indicates if the usage generated by this uptime has been sent for billing processing. | [optional] 
**created_at** | **datetime** | The date and time that the uptime record was created. | [optional] 
**ended_at** | **datetime** | The date and time that the transcoder was stopped for this uptime. If this value is not present, it indicates that the transcoder is currently running. | [optional] 
**id** | **str** | The unique alphanumeric string that identifies the uptime record. | [optional] 
**running** | **bool** | A Boolean value that indicates if the transcoder is still running for this uptime. | [optional] 
**started_at** | **datetime** | The date and time that the transcoder started for this uptime. | [optional] 
**transcoder_id** | **str** | The unique alphanumeric string that identifies the transcoder. | [optional] 
**updated_at** | **str** | The date and time that the uptime record was updated. | [optional]
